					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7007497#post-3915506</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7007497/redacted-for-questionable-reasons#post-3915506</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 18 Aug 2018 05:44:31 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>djkaktus</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1888434</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <div style="text-align: center;"> <p><em>When I walk in the club</em><br /> <em>All eyes on me</em><br /> <em>I'm with the party rock crew</em><br /> <em>All drinks are free</em><br /> <em>We like Ciroc, we love Patron</em><br /> <em>We came to party rock</em><br /> <em>Everybody its on</em></p> </div> <div style="text-indent:450px"> <p>&#8212;LMFAO</p> </div> <p>This was maybe a bad idea. You are all witnesses.</p> <p>Based on a <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/taboo">preposterously well-written 4K contest winner</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/peppersghost" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1553042&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1534571094" alt="PeppersGhost" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1553042)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/peppersghost" >PeppersGhost</a></span>.</p> <p>Also partly inspired by a 130 point disparity between that entry and the <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4444">arguably more handsome second place entry</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djkaktus" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1888434&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1534571094" alt="djkaktus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1888434)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djkaktus" >djkaktus</a></span>.</p> <p>Don't read too much into this. Or do, I'm not your dad.</p> <p>Sorry Peppersghost</p> <hr /> <p>Image credits:</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Show&nbsp;Credits</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Somebody&nbsp;please&nbsp;stop&nbsp;me&nbsp;god</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p><a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/gabrielap93/9779144082/">https://www.flickr.com/photos/gabrielap93/9779144082/</a></p> <p><a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Outhouse#/media/File:Lighthouse_Keeper%27s_Cottage_outhouse_(Cape_Florida_Lighthouse)_001.jpg">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Outhouse#/media/File:Lighthouse_Keeper%27s_Cottage_outhouse_(Cape_Florida_Lighthouse)_001.jpg</a></p> <p>also peppersghost made that top image so</p> </div> </div> </div> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
